Overview:
Peace, Love and Low Carb - Dips, Dressings and Sauces - 20 Low Carb, Paleo and Primal Recipes is the most recent book in Kyndra's series of mini-cookbooks. This book is full of delicious dip, dressing, and sauce recipes. You can ditch the store bought versions that are full of nasty chemicals and ingredients you can't even pronounce and start making healthier versions out of fresh, real food ingredients.
